{"word":"G3716 - ὀρθοποδέω - orthopodéō - or-thop-od-eh'-o - Walk uprightly","slug":"G3716","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὀρθοποδέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>orthopodéō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>or-thop-od-eh'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Walk uprightly"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03BF;&#x0313;&#x03C1;&#x03B8;&#x03BF;&#x03C0;&#x03BF;&#x03B4;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03C9; - orthopodeo&#x0304;</b> - <i>or-thop-od-eh'-o</i><p/>From a compound of <a href=\"#/G3717\">G3717</a> and <a href=\"#/G4228\">G4228</a>; to <i>be straight footed</i>, that is, (figuratively) to <i>go directly</i> forward: - walk uprightly."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1357\">G1357</a>, <a href=\"#/G1882\">G1882</a>, <a href=\"#/G3717\">G3717</a>, <a href=\"#/G3718\">G3718</a>, <a href=\"#/G3719\">G3719</a>, <a href=\"#/G3720\">G3720</a>, <a href=\"#/G3721\">G3721</a>, <a href=\"#/G3722\">G3722</a>, <a href=\"#/G3723\">G3723</a>"}]}